headline: 5 Top Dividend Stocks Yielding Over 5% to Buy for Passive Income
summary: Investing in dividend stocks can be a great way to collect dividend income.  Several high-quality companies currently offer higher-yielding dividends.  Here are five top dividend stocks currently yielding over 5%, well above the S&P 500's sub-1.5% dividend yield.
